Third Young Mistress,

40
00:02:38,710 --> 00:02:40,840
I wish to ask you for a favor.

41
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:42,630
Go ahead.

42
00:02:43,630 --> 00:02:46,800
I heard
that Yangzhou was famous for its embroidery.

43
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,360
Third Young Mistress,
you're a noble lady as well.

44
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,590
I'm sure you possess
top-tier needlework skills.

45
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:54,190
Please show me your skills today.

46
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,310
Xiaoqiao,

47
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,800
although the Du family isn't
as prestigious as the Qi family,

48
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:01,910
we're considered rich

49
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:03,630
in Yangzhou.

50
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,710
We hire embroiderers

51
00:03:05,710 --> 00:03:07,190
to make all the embroideries at home.

52
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,710
My mother said

53
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,080
that although we aren't that wealthy,

54
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:12,280
we don't lack the money
to hire embroiderers.

55
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,080
We're unlike poor families

56
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:15,870
that make the ladies at home
do their embroideries.

57
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,240
Poor families are quite petty.

58
00:03:19,030 --> 00:03:21,590
If so, Third Young Mistress,
what have you learned

59
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,910
when you were home?

60
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:26,310
Of course I learned everything there was.

61
00:03:26,910 --> 00:03:28,470
The Du family has a business.

62
00:03:29,310 --> 00:03:31,630
I have to learn how to manage businesses.

63
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:33,870
It's something like...

64
00:03:33,870 --> 00:03:34,870
Third Young Mistress,

65
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:37,280
you know how to manage businesses too?

66
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,750
It's not that difficult.

67
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,750
You just need to learn how to do business

68
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:42,910
and make money.

69
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:45,400
Third Young Mistress, you're amazing.

70
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,470
It's nothing noteworthy.

71
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:50,800
If so, did Mr. Du allow you
to manage the shops then?

72
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,840
Of course.

73
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:54,240
I managed all 18 of them before.

74
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,310
Xiaoqiao, here you go.

75
