100
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:38,270
I wouldn't be able to sleep or eat.

101
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:45,510
Shizhao is managing the shops well.

102
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:48,720
Old Madam,
it's all thanks to your guidance.

103
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:52,830
However, the Ke family is also waiting
for him to inherit

104
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:54,750
their family business in Jiangzhou.

105
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,800
I'm afraid

106
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:59,270
