107
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:06,310
I also gave it some thought before.

108
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,120
However, Tianlei

109
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:12,680
isn't capable enough
to be the head of the family yet.

110
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:21,600
Old Madam,

111
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:25,120
Third Young Master has found himself
a great assistant.

112
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,310
