113
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,190
It's Third Young Mistress.

114
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:31,750
Third Young Mistress?

115
00:06:34,750 --> 00:06:36,120
What's wrong with her?

116
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:39,040
Old Madam, did you have no idea?

117
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:42,040
Third Young Madam was managing
her family business in Yangzhou

118
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:45,270
instead of learning needlework.

119
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:48,480
Even her siblings were impressed
with her skills.

120
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:54,120
Who told you that?

121
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:56,360
Third Young Mistress told me that herself.

122
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,600
Your in-law, Mr. Du of Yangzhou,

123
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:02,270
entrusted all 18 shops to her care.

124
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,040
Is that true?

125
00:07:12,630 --> 00:07:14,360
That's great.

126
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,600
What do you think?

127
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:20,040
I got you

128
00:07:20,430 --> 00:07:21,870
such a capable daughter-in-law.

129
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:26,950
Old Madam,
it's all thanks to your excellent taste.

130
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,120
Summon Third Young Master

131
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,630
and Third Young Mistress.

132
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,430
We shall

133
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:37,270
test her.

134
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:39,920
All right.

135
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:43,480
Sunlight shines on the incense burner
as smoke purple rises.

136
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,120
Wrong.

137
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:50,120
From afar, I see waterfalls in front.

138
00:07:51,430 --> 00:07:52,310
