139
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,190
Show me your hand.

140
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:58,430
What?

141
00:08:01,070 --> 00:08:01,800
Just show it to me.

142
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:14,830
You're not supposed to get that wrong.

143
00:08:15,630 --> 00:08:16,270
Again.

144
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,000
Sunlight shines on the incense burner

145
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,120
as purple smoke rises.

146
00:08:29,270 --> 00:08:31,070
From afar, I see waterfalls

147
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,150
hanging before me.

148
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:36,120
The cascading waterfall
plummets three thousand feet,

149
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,440
as if the Milky Way
descends from the Ninth Heaven.

150
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:46,960
Show me your hand.

151
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:08,720
You rascal.

152
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,320
Fang Xiaoqiao is here.

153
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,120
Hurry, sit down.

154
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:18,960
Cough now.

155
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,120
Xiaoqiao, you're here.

156
00:09:30,750 --> 00:09:32,440
Third Young Mistress, Third Young Master.

157
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,440
So, you guys were reading just now?

158
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:35,870
I was looking for you guys.

159
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,320
What's the matter?

160
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,030
Old Madam is asking for you two.

161
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,030
What does Grandmother need from me?

162
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,000
In the Qi Residence,

163
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,630
whenever Old Madam summons you,

164
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:50,630
it's never a good thing.
It's also a huge deal.

165
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:56,550
All right.

166
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,840
Go back and tell Grandmother

167
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,790
that Bingyan and I will head there soon.

168
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:05,150
All right. I shall take my leave.

169
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:25,630
Grandmother.

170
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:26,150
Grandmother.

171
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:27,910
Mother.

172
00:10:27,910 --> 00:10:28,480
Mother.

173
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:31,550
Come and have a seat.

174
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,720
Have a seat.

175
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:33,600
Sit down.

176
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:40,120
Bingyan,

177
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:43,080
I heard that you managed 18 shops

178
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:45,720
when you were still
living with your family.

179
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,200
Is that true?

180
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:07,510
Yes, it's true.

181
00:11:14,550 --> 00:11:15,440
In the past,

182
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:19,360
I used to follow my father around.

183
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:23,150
I was observing him
when he was checking the accounts.

184
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,150
Due to that, my father

185
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,120
let me handle some of the shops.

186
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:41,000
And, since I was doing a good job at it,

187
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,240
he told me

188
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,910
that he would let me handle the business

189
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:46,320
when I turned 18.

190
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:50,720
How...

191
00:11:51,150 --> 00:11:52,030
How many shops did you say just now?

192
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,480
18.

193
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,200
Yes, I managed 18 shops.

194
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:57,320
That's right, 18 shops.

195
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,000
But after that...

196
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:02,670
I was married off to Linzhou

197
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:04,120
before I turned 18.

198
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:08,510
So, in reality, I haven't managed
to handle 18 shops yet.

199
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,750
That's quite all right.

200
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,510
You're a girl,

201
00:12:13,510 --> 00:12:15,000
yet you follow your father around

202
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:17,150
and manage his business for him
at such a young age.

203
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,080
I only started

204
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:22,200
managing the family business
when I was 25.

205
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:24,720
Tianlei,

206
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:26,550
this bride of yours

207
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:30,080
is much more capable than me
when I was young.

208
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:34,270
Have a seat.

209
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:42,030
So, what kinds of goods

210
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:44,030
were you guys selling?

211
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,360
Timbers.

212
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:01,960
Grandmother, we sold timbers.

213
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:06,360
So, your family was

214
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,630
in the timber industry?

215
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,440
But I've never heard
of your family's name before.

216
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:19,360
Grandmother, you have never heard
of our name before?

217
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:25,480
Actually, we sell more than just timbers.

218
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:27,240
Two of the shops I managed

219
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,510
were...

220
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:31,670
They sell the leftover wooden material

221
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:33,200
left behind by building
and furniture constructions.

222
00:13:33,630 --> 00:13:35,480
I thought it was a waste

223
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,790
to throw them away.

224
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:39,360
That's why I deliver them
to two of my shops

225
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:41,000
and sell them as firewood.

226
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:43,790
I never expected my staff
to be so adept at doing business.

227
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,120
The firewood sold like hotcakes.

228
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:49,080
After that, they bought
a huge piece of land in Yangzhou.

229
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:53,790
What are you laughing at?

230
00:13:53,790 --> 00:13:55,480
They did buy a huge piece of land
in Yangzhou.

231
00:14:01,630 --> 00:14:02,960
Not bad at all.

232
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,960
A young lass like you

233
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:07,240
is pretty good at doing business.

234
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:11,270
That's right. Business is all about
being smart and flexible.

235
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:14,790
Tianlei was born with a weak constitution.

236
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,670
In the future, I have to depend on you

237
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:20,030
for our family business.

238
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:24,750
By the way,

239
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:27,870
tomorrow

240
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:31,750
there'll be the financial audit
of all 14 of our shops in Linzhou.

241
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:34,790
You can be our host.

242
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,630
You can teach them how to do business.

243
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:40,750
Is that okay?

244
00:14:46,030 --> 00:14:47,270
Grandmother,

245
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:50,000
Bingyan is new to Linzhou.

246
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,510
She's not used to the place yet.

247
00:14:51,870 --> 00:14:52,840
I think

248
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:55,000
we should let Ke host the audit instead.

249
00:14:56,270 --> 00:14:59,030
We have to start somewhere, right?

250
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:00,150
That's right.

251
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,030
Grandmother,

252
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:08,550
Bingyan just married
into the Qi Residence not long ago.

253
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,080
And, she's young.

254
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,480
I don't think it's appropriate for her
to bear such an important position.

255
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,870
There's nothing inappropriate about it.

256
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:16,030
I think it's perfectly appropriate.

257
00:15:16,030 --> 00:15:18,200
It's decided then.

258
00:15:42,780 --> 00:15:44,690
[Garden of Harmony]

259
00:15:44,690 --> 00:15:46,170
[Figure something out for me.]

260
00:15:57,890 --> 00:15:58,500
Your Ladyship,

261
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:02,260
what's with all the sweat on your face?

262
00:16:04,020 --> 00:16:04,890
It's because she blew it.

263
00:16:05,530 --> 00:16:06,170
She blew it?

264
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:09,690
Why is she sweating
when the wind is blowing her?

265
00:16:11,770 --> 00:16:13,050
It's all because I bragged.

266
00:16:16,650 --> 00:16:17,860
Miss Bingyan

267
00:16:18,140 --> 00:16:20,290
is too much of a braggart.

268
00:16:20,620 --> 00:16:23,380
She said she managed 18 shops in Yangzhou.

269
00:16:23,460 --> 00:16:25,500
Old Madam was so happy
when she heard that.

270
00:16:25,570 --> 00:16:26,810
She plans to test her tomorrow.

271
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:29,260
She wants her
to attend the financial audit

272
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:30,260
of all 14 of our shops tomorrow.

273
00:16:32,810 --> 00:16:35,380
